      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-2">
        Website by <a href="https://staticfish.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors inline-flex items-center">
          StaticFish <ExternalLink class="w-3 h-3 ml-1" />
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>